{"tid":1744771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要記住 投白票=放生建制保皇狗","createTime":"2019-11-22T01:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:14:06.000Z","uid":53675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a776e11f4bcaf975ad2f0dc8d9a852d8119f44be","tid":1744771,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"係人都知一到選舉前啲分化同帶風向五毛就會出曬嚟 <br />\n轆過幾個選舉po啲仆街有兩大理據<br />\n<br />\n1 民主派出賣港人 一票不投民主派<br />\n2 唔係要焦土嘅咩 焦土就係投白票<br />\n<br />\n我想同大家講 今次選舉我哋目的只有一個 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不求民主派贏，只求建制派輸！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家手上有票唔用 人哋建制派就已經計好曬票 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投白票必然唔係焦土而係放生建制派</span></span>呢一點其實顯然易見 所以三毛同熱狗真係好易分得出 <br />\n<br />\n星期日可以話係藍絲最團結嘅一日 所以 我誠心懇請咁多位手足 大家可以同仇敵愾 槍口對外 目標一致咁 先踢走保皇黨 後而整頓內在 多謝各位<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"5c66b282885fda72e1be96e9b612a8851c63dc5c","tid":1744771,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:56:18.000Z","msg":"自推（1/10）"},{"pid":"ccba0f0e0c65c627b3c83fa2d4d08a310b327a7d","tid":1744771,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:56:30.000Z","msg":"自推（2/10）"},{"pid":"0b33ea4805cb9d69c12fe9301018717194cb2f32","tid":1744771,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:56:41.000Z","msg":"自推（3/10）"},{"pid":"3c85f8a56d9c169cc7dd114ab5ca89529d23911e","tid":1744771,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:56:51.000Z","msg":"自推（3/10）"},{"pid":"80ed71aba291a61a1d428f2264d65afae7b21a26","tid":1744771,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:57:07.000Z","msg":"自推（4/10）"},{"pid":"4455c7893a323b4b60e49010651a23ae9ac3303c","tid":1744771,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:57:20.000Z","msg":"自推（5/10）"},{"pid":"1ba3c88589060603be43f85a02efc1be